ng%20for%20a%20report%20by%20this%20morning%20on%20the%20status%20of%20all%20the%20complaints%20by%20the%20woman%20judge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Secretary%20General%20was%20informed%20on%20the%20phone%20last%20night%20that%20the%20acting%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20the%20High%20Court%20had%20also%20taken%20note%20of%20the%20open%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20judge%20said%20in%20her%20letter%20that%20a%20probe%20was%20ordered%20into%20her%20allegations%20after%20she%20filed%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20Internal%20Complaints%20Committee%20of%20the%20High%20Court%20in%20July%202023%2C%20but%20the%20inquiry%20is%20%26quot%3Ba%20farce%20and%20a%20sham%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20witnesses%20in%20the%20enquiry%20are%20immediate%20Subordinates%20of%20the%20District%20Judge.%20How%20the%20Committee%20expects%20the%20Witnesses%20to%20depose%20against%20their%20Boss%20is%20beyond%20my%20understanding%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20she%20had%20requested%20the%20transfer%20of%20the%20judge%20pending%20the%20inquiry%20to%20ensure%20fair%20investigation%2C%20but%20her%20petition%20was%20dismissed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20%26quot%3Bjust%20eight%20seconds.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20I%20requested%20was%20that%20the%20District%20Judge%20be%20transferred%20during%20the%20pendency%20of%20the%20inquiry.%20The%20bare%20minimum%20prayer%20was%20not%20heeded%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20no%20will%20to%20live%20anymore.%20I%20have%20been%20rendered%20to%20a%20Walking%20Corpse%20in%20the%20last%20year%20and%20a%20half.%20There%20is%20no%20purpose%20in%20carrying%20this%20soulless%20and%20lifeless%20body%20around%20anymore.%20There%20is%20no%20purpose%20left%20in%20my%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20two-page%20letter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702612020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F20