azal%20Alagh%20(%40GhazalAlagh)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGhazalAlagh%2Fstatus%2F1735261074633662656%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2014%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20debate%20started%20last%20week%20when%20Union%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%20Minister%20Smriti%20Irani%2C%20while%20responding%20to%20Congress%20MP%20Shashi%20Tharoor%2C%20told%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20that%20there%20is%20%26quot%3Bno%20proposal%20under%20the%20consideration%20of%20the%20government%20to%20make%20provision%20for%20paid%20menstrual%20leave%20mandatory%20for%20all%20workplaces%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20came%20up%20again%20on%20Wednesday%20when%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20leader%20Manoj%20Jha%20posed%20a%20question%20%C2%A0on%20the%20menstrual%20hygiene%20policy%20in%20the%20upper%20house.%20He%20asked%20if%20the%20government%20was%20taking%20any%20measures%20to%20make%20it%20compulsory%20for%20employers%20to%20provide%20menstrual%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Ms%20Irani%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAs%20a%20menstruating%20woman%2C%20menstruation%20and%20the%20menstruation%20cycle%20is%20not%20a%20handicap%2C%20it's%20a%20natural%20part%20of%20women's%20life%20journey...%20We%20should%20not%20propose%20issues%20where%20women%20are%20denied%20equal%20opportunities%20just%20because%20somebody%20who%20does%20not%20menstruate%20has%20a%20particular%20viewpoint%20towards%20menstruation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20and%20Family%20Welfare%20has%20formulated%20a%20draft%20menstrual%20hygiene%20policy%20in%20consultation%20with%20stakeholders%2C%20Ms%20Irani%20informed%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702611540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fjenephp_ghazal-alagh-twitter_625x300_15_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmama-earth-founder-gh