anonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-67723936%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-67723936.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-67723936.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mahadev%20App%20Case%3A%20Actor%20Sahil%20Khan%2C%203%20Others%20Summoned%20For%20Questioning%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Special%20Investigating%20Team%20(SIT)%20of%20Mumbai%20cyber%20cell%2C%20which%20is%20investigating%20the%20Rs%2015%2C000%20crore%20Mahadev%20App%20online%20betting%20case%2C%20has%20issued%20summons%20to%20actor%20Sahil%20Khan%20and%20three%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20been%20instructed%20to%20appear%20before%20the%20SIT%20on%20Friday%20for%20questioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Dubai%20Police%20on%20Tuesday%20arrested%20Ravi%20Uppal%2C%20one%20of%20the%20two%20prime%20accused%20in%20the%20Mahadev%20Book%20online%20betting%20syndicate.%20Uppal%20is%20also%20the%20alleged%20co-promoter%20of%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20sources%2C%20the%20arrest%20was%20made%20by%20Dubai%20police%20based%20on%20a%20red%20corner%20notice%20issued%20by%20Interpol%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20ED.%20Uppal%20will%20be%20extradited%20to%20India%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUppal%20is%20facing%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%20being%20probed%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate.%20He%20is%20named%20as%20accused%20in%20the%20case%20in%20which%20allegations%20of%20kickbacks%20were%20made%20against%20outgoing%20Chhattisgarh%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhupesh%20Baghel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20officials%2C%20Dubai%20Police%20arrested%20Uppal%20following%20a%20Red%20Corner%20notice%20issued%20against%20him%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20that%20Dubai%20authorities%20conveyed%20this%20to%20Indian%20officials%20soon%20after%20the%20arrest%20of%20Uppal%20and%20showed%20their%20willingness%20to%20deport%20him%2C%20as%20he%20is%20wanted%20in%20India%20for%20his%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20money%20laundering%20worth%20nearly%20Rs%206%2C000%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERed%20Corner%20notices%20were%20issued%20against%20Uppal%20and%20Sourabh%20Chandrakar%2C%20the%20other%20promoter%20and%20mastermind%20of%20the%20illegal%20betting%20syndicate%2C%20who%20is%20also%20in%20the%20UAE%2C%20in%20October%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Red%20Corner%20notice%20was%20issued%20against%20both%20of%20the%20accused%20after%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20moved%20a%20special%20court%20in%20Raipur%20and%20obtained%20a%20non-bailable%20warrant%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20arrest%20of%20Uppal%2C%20it%20is%20learned%20that%20Chandrakar%20may%20be%20arrested%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20development%20comes%20months%20after%20a%20lavish%20wedding%20held%20this%20February%20in%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20caught%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%2C%20as%20the%20entire%20money%20around%20Rs%20200%20crore%20spent%20on%20the%20bash%20was%20paid%20entirely%20in%20cash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20his%20wedding%20held%20in%20Ras%20AlKhaimah%2C%20Chandrakar%20hired%20private%20jets%20to%20ferry%20family%20members%20from%20Nagpur%20to%20the%20UAE%20and%20paid%20celebrities%20from%20the%20film%20industry%20to%20perform%2C%20according%20to%20the%20ED.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Mahadev%20betting%20app%20case%2C%20there%20are%20allegations%20of%20fraud%20of%2015%2C000%20crore%20rupees%20along%20with%20match-fixing%2C%20illegal%20hawala%2C%20and%20cryptocurrency%20transactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20had%20filed%20a%20charge%20sheet%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20Mahadev%20online%20betting%20app%20case.%20According%20to%20the%20officials%2C%2014%20accused%20have%20been%20named%20in%20the%20charge%20sheet%2C%20namely%20Sourabh%20Chandrakar%2C%20Ravi%20Uppal%2C%20Vikas%20Chhapariya%2C%20Chandra%20Bhushan%20Verma%2C%20Satish%20Chandrakar%2C%20Anil%20Dammani%2C%20Sunil%20Dammani%2C%20Vishal%20Ahuja%2C%20Dheeraj%20Ahuja%2C%20Srijan%20Associates%20through%20Punaram%20Verma%2C%20Shiv%20Kumar%20Verma%2C%20Punaram%20Verma%20Shiv%20Kumar%20Verma%2C%20Yashoda%20Verma%20and%20Pawan%20Nathani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%2C%20the%20Mahadev%20Online%20Book%20Betting%20app%20is%20an%20umbrella%20syndicate%20arranging%20online%20platforms%20for%20enabling%20illegal%20betting%20websites%20to%20enroll%20new%20users%2C%20create%20user%20IDs%2C%20and%20launder%20money%20through%20a%20layered%20web%20of%20Benami%20bank%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20in%20mid-September%20this%20year%20released%20details%20of%20its%20investigation%20into%20the%20online%20money%20laundering%20case%20linked%20with%20the%20Mahadev%20Online%20Book%20Betting%20App.%20Wedding%20planners%2C%20dancers%2C%20decorators%20etc%2C%20were%20hired%20from%20Mumbai%20and%20hawala%20channels%20were%20allegedly%20used%20to%20make%20payments%20in%20cash%2C%20the%20agency%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20said%20Chandrakar%20and%20Ravi%20Uppal%20who%20hail%20from%20Bhilai%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20are%20the%20two%20main%20promoters%20of%20the%20Mahadev%20betting%20platform%20and%20ran%20their%20operations%20from%20Dubai.%20They%20had%20created%20an%20empire%20for%20themselves%20in%20that%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20had%20recently%20conducted%20searches%20at%2039%20locations%20across%20Raipur%2C%20Bhopal%2C%20Mumbai%20and%20Kolkata%20and%20seized%20illegal%20assets%20worth%20Rs%20417%20crore.%20ED%20has%20also%20earnestly%20taken%20up%20investigation%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA)%20special%20court%20at%20Raipur%20has%20also%20issued%20non-bailable%20warrants%20against%20the%20suspects.%20The%20ED%20which%20is%20investigating%20money%20laundering%20charges%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20Mahadev%20Online%20Book%20app%20had%20also%20conducted%20searches%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20arrested%20four%20accused%20including%20the%20chief%20liaisoner%20of%20the%20betting%20syndicate%2C%20which%20the%20probe%20agency%20alleged%20was%20organizing%20payment%20of%20bribes%20to%20senior%20government%20functionaries%20as%20'protection%20money'.%20ED%20had%20stated%20that%20it%20has%20successfully%20identified%20other%20major%20players%20involved%20in%20the%20money%20laundering%20operations%20of%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Directorate%20of%20Enforcement%20(ED)%20is%20investigating%20the%20Mahadev%20Book%20Online%20Betting%20APP%20syndicate%2C%20in%20which%20the%20promoters%20of%20this%20betting%20syndicate%20are%20allegedly%20sitting%20abroad%20and%20remotely%20running%20thousands%20of%20panels%20across%20India%20with%20the%20help%20of%20their%20friends%20and%20associates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702610940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2Frtenb1r_sahil-khan-1200_625x300_19_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmahadev-app-betting-case-actor-sahil-khan-three-others-summoned-for-questioning-today-4676988%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Special%20Investigating%20Team%20(SIT)%20of%20Mumbai%20cyber%20cell%2C%20which%20is%20investigating%20the%20Rs%2015%2C000%20crore%20Mahadev%20App%20online%20betting%20case%2C%20has%20issued%20summons%20to%20actor%20Sahil%20Khan%20and%20three%20others.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmahadev-app-betting-case-actor-sahil-khan-three-others-summoned-for-questioning-today-4676988%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww