0to%20uproot%20Hamas%20and%20a%20land%2C%20sea%20and%20air%20offensive%20has%20been%20ongoing%20for%20the%20last%20three%20months%20and%20over%2018%2C500%20people%20have%20died%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20wished%20Hamas%20on%20its%2036th%20foundation%20day%20but%20with%20a%20message%2C%20hoping%20it's%20the%20Palestinian%20group's%20%26quot%3Blast%20birthday%26quot%3B.%20In%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20Israel%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHamas%20was%20founded%2036%20years%20ago.%20May%20this%20birthday%20be%20its%20last.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EHamas%20was%20founded%2036%20years%20ago%20today.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMay%20this%20birthday%20be%20its%20last.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FFreeGazaFromHamas%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23FreeGazaFromHamas%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FwsT6QWG1i1%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FwsT6QWG1i1%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Israel%20%D7%99%D7%A9%D7%A8%D7%90%D7%9C%20%F0%9F%87%AE%F0%9F%87%B1%20(%40Israel)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIsrael%2Fstatus%2F1735352227403907212%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EDecember%2014%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20put%20rockets%20instead%20of%20candles%20for%20Hamas'%20%26quot%3B36th%20birthday%26quot%3B%20and%20called%20for%20freeing%20Gaza%20from%20Hamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGaza%20Food%20Crisis%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20in%20Gaza%20are%20begging%20for%20food%2C%20paying%2050%20times%20more%20than%20usual%20for%20a%20single%20can%20of%20beans%20and%20slaughtering%20donkeys%20to%20feed%20their%20families%20as%20the%20relentless%20bombardment%20for%20three%20months%20has%20crippled%20daily%20life%20and%20medical%20and%20food%20aid%20has%20been%20badly%20hit%20despite%20Israel's%20assurances%20of%20safe%20supply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20Humanitarian%20Office%20OCHA%20said%20limited%20aid%20distributions%20were%20taking%20place%20in%20the%20Rafah%20area%2C%20close%20to%20the%20border%20with%20Egypt%20in%20southern%20Gaza%2C%20where%20almost%20half%20of%20its%20population%20of%202.3%20million%20is%20now%20estimated%20to%20be%20living.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20aid%20distribution%20has%20largely%20stopped%2C%20due%20to%20the%20intensity%20of%20hostilities%20and%20restrictions%20on%20movement%20along%20the%20main%20roads%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENorth%20Gaza%2C%20which%20faced%20the%20initial%20brunt%20of%20Israel's%20all-out%20war%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20rubble%20and%20barely%20any%20aid%20has%20got%20through%20since%20a%20week-long%20truce%20ended%20on%20December%201.%20The%20UN%20estimates%201.9%20million%20out%20of%20Gaza's%202.4%20million%20people%20have%20been%20displaced.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20Israeli-occupied%20West%20Bank%20region%20is%20witnessing%20violence%20that%20has%20surged%20to%20an%20unseen%20level%20in%20almost%20two%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BRight%20To%20Self%20Defence%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20is%20facing%20mounting%20pressure%20over%20its%20stance%20defending%20Israel's%20right%20to%20self-defence%20and%20vetoed%20a%20UN%20Security%20Council%20resolution%20calling%20for%20a%20ceasefire.%20US%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20Jake%20Sullivan%20told%20Israel%20to%20scale%20down%20its%20war%20on%20Hamas%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bnear%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20with%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20urging%20it%20to%20take%20more%20care%20to%20save%20civilian%20lives%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Defense%20Minister%20Yoav%20Gallant%20warned%20Sullivan%20that%20Israel's%20fight%20with%20Hamas%20%26quot%3Bwill%20require%20a%20period%20--%20it%20will%20last%20more%20than%20several%20months%2C%20but%20we%20will%20win%20and%20we%20will%20destroy%20them.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoe%20Biden%20issued%20his%20strongest%20criticism%20yet%20of%20Israel%2C%20warning%20that%20Israel%20risked%20losing%20global%20support%20over%20%26quot%3Bindiscriminate%20bombing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20vowed%20to%20carry%20on%20%26quot%3Buntil%20victory%26quot%3B%20and%20Foreign%20Minister%20Eli%20Cohen%20said%20the%20war%20would%20continue%20%26quot%3Bwith%20or%20without%20international%20support%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20prime%20minister%20has%20said%20there%20is%20also%20%26quot%3Bdisagreement%26quot%3B%20with%20Washington%20over%20how%20Gaza%20would%20be%20governed%20after%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702608600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fsjk7knv8_israel-_625x300_15_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmay-this-birthday-be-its-last-israel-on-hamas-36th-founding-day-4676984%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Israel's%20bombing%20of%20Gaza%20continues%20as%20its%20war%20against%20Hamas%2C%20the%20Palestinian%20group%20that%20carried%20out%20unprecedented%20attacks%20on%20Israel%20on%20October%207%2C%20in%20which%20over%201%2C200%20people%20were%20killed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmay-this-birthday-be-its-last-israel-on-hamas-36th-founding-day-4676984%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmay-this-birthday-be-its-last-israel-on-hamas-36th-founding-day-4676984%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmay-this-birthday-be-its-last-israel-on-hamas-36th-founding-day-4676984%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22MS%20Dhoni's%20No.%207%20Jersey%20Retired%2C%20BCCI%20Informs%20Team%20India%20Stars%3A%20Sources%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPaying%2