ider.com%2Fisrael-pounding-gaza-massive-spice-kit-bombs-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E(SPICE)%20bombs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20are%20weapons%20equipped%20with%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIsraeli-developed%20guidance%20kits%20that%2C%20similar%20to%20JDAMs%2C%20convert%20air-to-ground%20unguided%20bombs%20into%20precision-guided%20munitions.%20Bombs%20with%20either%20SPICEs%20or%20JDAMs%20are%20generally%20considered%20to%20be%20highly%20accurate%2C%20but%20the%20extreme%20wide%20area%20affected%20by%20the%20blast%20raises%20concerns%2C%20weapons%20investigators%20told%20BI's%20Jake%20Epstein.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20use%20of%20such%20devastating%20weapons%2C%20along%20with%20the%20IDF's%20revelations%20that%20it%20uses%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-lets-ai-decide-what-it-should-bomb-increasing-the-number-of-targets-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eartificial%20intelligence%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20determine%20where%20in%20Gaza%20it%20should%20bomb%2C%20have%20been%20seen%20by%20some%20observers%20as%20cause%20for%20concern.%20That%20system%20is%20part%20of%20an%20operation%20known%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Btarget%20factory%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20has%20increased%20the%20number%20of%20strike%20locations%20by%20over%2070%2C000%20percent%20since%20it%20first%20became%20functional%20several%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20late%20November%2C%20a%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emedia%20investigation%20by%20the%20left-wing%20Israeli%20outlet%20%2B972%20Magazine%20into%20the%20role%20of%20the%20AI%20system%2C%20called%20%26quot%3BGospel%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20airstrikes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.972mag.com%2Fmass-assassination-factory-israel-calculated-bombing-gaza%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efound%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20produces%20recommendations%20for%20targeting%20homes%20or%20areas%20where%20suspected%20Hamas%20or%20Palestinian%20Islamic%20Jihad%20militants%20might%