%20weakened%20US%20and%20cost%20US%20taxpayers%20an%20%26quot%3Bastronomical%26quot%3B%20sum%20to%20pay%20for%20beefed-up%20defense%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Institute%20for%20the%20Study%20of%20War%20(ISW)%2C%20a%20Washington%2C%20DC-based%20think%20tank%2C%20warned%20that%20if%20Russia%20wins%2C%20the%20United%20States%20would%20be%20forced%20to%20move%20American%20troops%20and%20stealth%20jets%20to%20Eastern%20Europe%2C%20stretching%20the%20US%20so%20thin%20that%20it%20could%20allow%20for%20China%20to%20claim%20Taiwan%2C%20expanding%20its%20territory%20and%20influence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.understandingwar.org%2Fbackgrounder%2Fhigh-price-losing-ukraine%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20lengthy%20assessment%20published%20on%20Thursday%20that%20the%20US%20%26quot%3Bhas%20a%20much%20higher%20stake%26quot%3B%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fputin-orders-russia-troops-to-ukraine-major-escalation-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERussian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin's%20grinding%2C%20nearly%20two-year%20war%20with%20Ukraine%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3Bthan%20most%20people%20think.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20war%20analysts%20argued%20that%20if%20Western%20aid%20to%20Ukraine%20were%20to%20suddenly%20be%20cut%20%E2%80%94as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fputin-hide-his-pleasure-over-republican-moves-block-ukraine-aid-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERepublicans%20in%20Congress%20are%20now%20threatening%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20it%20%26quot%3Bwould%20likely%20lead%20sooner%20or%20later%20to%20the%20collapse%20of%20Ukraine's%20ability%20to%20hold%20off%20the%20Russian%20military%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20ultimately%20allow%20Putin%20to%20take%20over%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHelping%20Ukraine%20hold%20the%20line%20against%20Russian%20forces%20through%20Western%20military%20aid%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bfar%20more%20advantageous%20and%20cheaper%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20US%20than%20if%20Ukraine%20were%20to%20lose%20the%20war%2C%20according%20to%20the%20war%20experts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepublicans%20in%20the%20US%20Congress%20have%20been%20blocking%20new%20aid%20to%20Ukraine%2C%20with%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fbriefing-room%2Fspeeches-remarks%2F2023%2F12%2F13%2Fremarks-by-president-biden-and-president-zelenskyy-of-ukraine-in-joint-press-conference-2%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccusing%3C%2Fa%3E%20them%20of%20holding%20the%20funding%20%26quot%3Bhostage%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20%26quot%3Bforce%20through%20an%20extreme%20Republican%20partisan%20agenda%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20US-Mexico%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20Republicans%20say%20they%20want%20tougher%20immigration%20politics%20and%20more%20funding%20for%20border%20security%20in%20exchange%20for%20helping%20Ukraine%2C%20other%20right-wing%20lawmakers%20have%20ruled%20out%20giving%20Ukraine%20any%20more%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20ISW%2C%20a%20Russian%20take-over%20of%20all%20of%20Ukraine%20%26quot%3Bis%20by%20no%20means%20impossible%26quot%3B%20if%20the%20US%20cuts%20off%20all%20military%20aid%20and%20Europe%20follows%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuch%20an%20outcome%20would%20bring%20a%20battered%20but%20triumphant%20Russian%20army%20right%20up%20to%20NATO's%20border%20from%20the%20Black%20Sea%20to%20the%20Arctic%20Ocean%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20war%20experts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20would%20mean%20that%20the%20US%20would%20be%20forced%20to%20deploy%20a%20%26quot%3Bsizable%20portion%26quot%3B%20of%20its%20ground%20forces%20to%20Eastern%20Europe%20to%20%26quot%3Bdeter%20and%20defend%20against%20a%20renewed%20Russian%20threat%20following%20a%20full%20Russian%20victory%2C%26quot%3B%20ISW%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20US%20would%20have%20to%20station%20a%20large%20number%20of%20stealth%20aircra