-contract-on-use-of-ai-heres-what-the-agreement-says%2Farticleshow%2F106001071.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Microsoft%20has%20agreed%20to%20include%20an%20AI%20article%20in%20a%20collective%20bargaining%20agreement%20with%20the%20Communications%20Workers%20of%20America%20(CWA)%2C%20allowing%20workers%20to%20challenge%20the%20company's%20use%20of%20AI.%20The%20agreement%20incorporates%20Microsoft's%20AI%20principles%20and%20commits%20to%20applying%20them%20across%20all%20AI%20technologies.%20It%20also%20obliges%20Microsoft%20to%20inform%20the%20union%20of%20any%20potential%20impact%20of%20AI%20or%20automation%20on%20union%20members'%20work%20and%20to%20negotiate%20over%20the%20impact%20on%20employees.%20The%20CWA%20president%20emphasized%20the%20importance%20of%20preserving%20unions'%20rights%20in%20the%20face%20of%20technological%20advancements.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fmicrosoft-agrees-to-employee-union-contract-on-use-of-ai-heres-what-the-agreement-says%2Farticleshow%2F106001071.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Boy%2C%2013%2C%20Charged%20After%20Allegedly%20Plotting%20A%20Mass%20Shooting%20At%20Synagogue%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%2013-year-old%20boy%20is%20facing%20criminal%20charges%20for%20allegedly%20planning%20a%20mass%20shooting%20at%20a%20synagogue%20in%20Ohio%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2023%2F12%2F14%2Fnews%2Fboy-13-charged-with-planning-mass-shooting-at-synagogue%2F%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Post%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3Ereported.%20According%20to%20court%20documents%2C%20the%20teenager%20was%20allegedly%20devising%20a%20plan%20to%20''complete%20a%20mass%20shooting''%20at%20Temple%20Israel%20in%20Canton%2C%20Ohio%20in%20September.%20He%20posted%20detailed%20plans%20of%20the%20attack%20on%20Discord%2C%20a%20messaging%20platform%20popular%20among%20gamers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20boy's%20alleged%20plot%20was%20discovered%20on%20September%201%20after%20Discord%20reported%20the%20teenager%20to%20the%20FBI.%20The%20investigation%20led%20to%20the%20teenager's%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDiscord's%20Counter-Extremism%20analysts%20proactively%20detected%2C%20removed%2C%20and%20reported%20this%20user%20to%20the%20FBI's%20National%20Threat%20Operations%20Center%2C%20which%20is%20what%20led%20to%20the%20user's%20arrest.%20We%20have%20a%20zero-tolerance%20policy%20against%20hate%20and%20violent%20extremism%2C%20and%20when%20we%20see%20it%2C%20we%20take%20immediate%20action.%20It%20is%20a%20top%20priority%20for%20Discord%20to%20ensure%20a%20safe%20experience%20for%20our%20users%2C%26quot%3B%20John%20Redgrave%2C%20Discord's%20vice%20president%20of%20trust%C2%A0%26amp%3B%20safety%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabcnews.go.com%2FUS%2Fdiscord-tips-off-fbi-13-year-olds-synagogue%2Fstory%3Fid%3D105647160%5C%22%3EABC%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20boy%2C%20who%20has%20not%20been%20publicly%20named%20because%20he's%20a%20minor%2C%20now%20faces%20juvenile%20misdemeanor%20charges%20of%20inducing%20panic%20and%20disorderly%20conduct.%20He%20is%20set%20to%20go%20to%20trial%20on%20December%2020%20in%20Stark%20County%20Family%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20it%20is%20unclear%20whether%20any%20weapons%20were%20found%20when%20the%20teenager%20was%20arrested%2C%20and%20how%20serious%20his%20intentions%20were.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%C2%A0statement%C2%A0from%20the%20Anti-Defamation%20League's%20chapter%20in%20Cleveland%2C%20about%2060%20miles%20from%20Ohio%2C%20said%20the%20group%20was%20''horrified''%20to%20learn%20of%20the%20plans%20to%20shoot%20up%20Temple%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''For%20young%20people%20like%20this%20suspect%2C%20we%20hope%20this%20can%20be%20a%20teachable%20moment.%20Hate%20and%20threats%20on%20social