0The%20Speaker%20and%20the%20ruling%20party%2C%20officials%20and%20even%20the%20media%20are%20calling%20it%20a%20security%20breach.%20Yet%20the%20five%20arrested%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fparliament-security-breach-rajnath-singh-opposition-statement-amit-shah%5C%22%3Ehave%20been%20booked%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20the%20draconian%20anti-terror%20law%2C%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%20and%20could%20even%20be%20booked%20for%20sedition.%20There%20is%20no%20evidence%20so%20far%20of%20the%20accused%20having%20links%20with%20any%20terror%20organisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20was%20at%20pains%20to%20point%20out%20that%20the%20security%20of%20Parliament%20is%20his%20responsibility.%20Yet%20the%20government%20has%20ordered%20a%20high-level%20probe%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fmha-orders-probe-into-parliament-security-breach-incident-2809994%5C%22%3Eheaded%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Anish%20Dayal%20Singh%2C%20CRPF%20chief.%20Incidentally%2C%20perimeter%20security%20of%20Parliament%20comes%20under%20the%20paramilitary%20force%20that%20Singh%20heads.%20The%20probe%20panel%20includes%20the%20Delhi%20Police%2C%20which%20is%20responsible%20for%20frisking%20visitors%20to%20Parliament%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Members%20of%20Parliament%20refused%20to%20let%20both%20Houses%20function%2C%2014%20opposition%20MPs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fparliament-security-breach-rajnath-singh-opposition-statement-amit-shah%5C%22%3Ehave%20been%20suspended%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20Derek%20O%E2%80%99Brien%20from%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20So%20far%2C%20no%20action%20has%20been%20taken%20against%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%E2%80%99s%20Mysuru%20MP%20Pratap%20Simha%2C%20who%20issued%20the%20visitors%20gallery%20pass%20to%20the%20two%20men%20who%20intruded%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20Many%20pointed%20to%20the%20expulsion%20of%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%2C%20Mahua%20Moitra%2C%20for%20sharing%20her%20credentials%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20website%20with%20her%20staff.%20The%20number%20was%20initially%2015%20till%20the%20Speaker%E2%80%99s%20office%20realised%20that%20one%20of%20the%20MPs%20was%20not%20even%20in%20town%20when%20he%20was%20suspended%20for%20disrupting%20the%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwhat-yellow-smoke-signals-tell-us-about-the-mother-of-democracy%5C%22%3EWhat%20Yellow%20Smoke%20Signals%20Tell%20Us%20About%20the%20%E2%80%98Mother%20of%20Democracy%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESivaganga%20MP%20Karti%20Chidambaram%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20this%20government%2C%20it%20is%20business%20as%20usual.%20They%20are%20behaving%20as%20if%20we%20are%20hallucinating%20and%20nothing%20really%20happened.%20They%20are%20trying%20to%20underplay%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20situation.%20The%20gas%20could%20have%20been%20lethal.%20The%20fact%20is%2C%20this%20was%20meticulously%20planned.%20They%20beat%20the%20system%20and%20the%20so-called%20foolproof%20security.%20And%20now%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20knee-jerk%20reaction.%20Ban%20visitors%2C%20ban%20journalists%20is%20their%20answer%20as%20is%20banning%20MPs%2C%20one%20of%20whom%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20even%20present%20there.%20This%20government%20cant%20recognise%20one%20Tamil%20from%20another.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20eight%20persons%20on%20deputation%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Secretariat%20have%20been%20suspended%20and%20security%20beefed%20up.%20The%20%3Cem%3Emakar%20dwar%3C%2Fem%3E%20used%20by%20visitors%20and%20MPs%20alike%20is%20out%20of%20bounds%20for%20journalists%2C%20and%20visitors%20are%20banned%20altogether%2C%20as%20is%20the%20staff%20of%20MPs.%20Access%20control%20to%20the%20complex%20has%20been%20tightened%20with%20pass%20holders%20being%20allowed%20in%20only%20from%20the%20transport%20bhavan%20side%20and%20Delhi%20Police%20could%20be%20seen%20fr